Text: Thanks for changing your mind about not uploading anymore Spidey books! I, for one, am enjoying this story.
Thank you so much for this!
I'll upload Amazing spider-man # 700 a little later,great scan,but also big size - 185 MB,just so you know...

Wait A Second, You were gonna stop putting up Spider-Man comics? Was it 'cause (SPOILER ALERT) Pete dies and Doc. Ock takes his place? Sure it sucks and Spider-Man will never be the same, but I'm willing to give it a try.....I miss Pete already.
